name: Fast Animals Slow Children
description:
1 VS 1 game where a slow child is chased by a fast animal.

CHILD:

Arrows - Move

ANIMAL:

WASD - Charge leap
V - Leap (After 3 seconds of charging, leap with maximum force automatically)

Child must survive for 3 minute!
